{"title":"Poc Ventral Lite: Poc launches lightest ever helmet","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/9263/poc-ventral-lite-poc-launches-lightest-ever-helmet","date":1614016735000,"content":"<span class=\"field field-name-field-author field-type-node-reference field-label-hidden\">\n      <span class=\"field-item even\"><a href=\"/authors/will-strickson\">Will Strickson</a></span>\n  </span><div class=\"field field-name-field-published-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden\">  \n  <div class=\"field-items\">      <div class=\"field-item even\"><span class=\"date-display-single\" property=\"v:dtreviewed\" datatype=\"xsd:dateTime\" content=\"2021-02-23T14:00:00+00:00\">Tuesday, February 23, 2021 - 14:00</span></div>    </div></div><p class=\"short-teaser\">\nDesigned for climbing and hot weather rides, Poc&#039;s new lightweight performance helmet will make its debut at Paris-Nice</p>\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-price field-type-text field-label-hidden\">  \n  <div class=\"field-items\">      <div class=\"field-item even\">£240</div>    </div></div><div class=\"field field-name-body\">\n      <p> Poc has launched the Ventral Lite, its 'lightest ever' cycling helmet, designed for climbing and riding in hot conditions.</p>\n<p>Since releasing its first cycling helmet in 2014, Poc has made its way to the forefront of helmet design, both technically and aesthetically – having been <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/8771/palace-skateboards-and-rapha-collaborate-for-education-first-kit-at-giro-ditalia\" target=\"_blank\">host to a large duck</a> during last year's <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/giro-ditalia\">Giro d'Italia</a>.</p>\n<p>That original helmet, the Octal, was designed to find the optimum combination of safety, performance and light weight and the Ventral Lite takes inspiration from the Octal with that same objective.</p>\n<p>Poc's head of product, Oscar Huss, said: 'We wanted to take the ideas and concepts from the Octal even further. Riders who are focussed on climbing or ride in hotter conditions are extremely conscious about weight, ventilation and comfort, which is where the Ventral Lite, our lightest ever helmet will excel.'</p>\n<p><div class=\"referenced-gallery-node\"><div class=\"picture type-image file-gallery-adv-full\" data-delta=\"2\">\n  <a href=\"/news/9264/poc-ventral-lite-photos#2\" data-gallery-id=\"9264\" data-count=\"18\"><p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 3 of</span> 18</p><img typeof=\"foaf:Image\" src=\"https://cdn1.cyclist.co.uk/sites/cyclist/files/styles/gallery_adv/public/2021/02/mj_poc_d2_2021_577.jpg?itok=A1kCgyQz\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 3 of </span>18</p>\n</div> </p>\n<h3>What's in the Poc?</h3>\n<p>From the template of the Ventral Air, Poc has stripped away any hint of excess weight, refining even the straps, while keeping it as safe as possible.</p>\n<p>While the redesigning of the shell and liner gives the Ventral Lite better structural integrity than its predecessor, it's the weight saving of the precisely cut outer shell and lower-density EPS foam that Poc wants you to get excited about.</p>\n<p>On top of that, it features a new minimalist size adjustment system and optimised straps that are, of course, more lightweight.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pocsports.com/collections/cycling-helmets-road/products/ventral-lite\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Buy the Poc Ventral Lite now</strong></em></a></p>\n<p><div class=\"referenced-gallery-node\"><div class=\"picture type-image file-gallery-adv-full\" data-delta=\"7\">\n  <a href=\"/news/9264/poc-ventral-lite-photos#7\" data-gallery-id=\"9264\" data-count=\"18\"><p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 8 of</span> 18</p><img typeof=\"foaf:Image\" src=\"https://cdn1.cyclist.co.uk/sites/cyclist/files/styles/gallery_adv/public/2021/02/poc_ventrallite_uraniumblack_basaltblue_matt_v005.0003.png?itok=ksV3R1qs\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 8 of </span>18</p>\n</div> </p>\n<p>'We strongly believe that the safest helmet is the one you choose to wear, one which you always look forward to wearing,' Huss says.</p>\n<p>'The Ventral Lite will provide the protection those riders deserve without ever noticing it's there.'</p>\n<p><div class=\"referenced-gallery-node\"><div class=\"picture type-image file-gallery-adv-full\" data-delta=\"1\">\n  <a href=\"/news/9264/poc-ventral-lite-photos#1\" data-gallery-id=\"9264\" data-count=\"18\"><p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 2 of</span> 18</p><img typeof=\"foaf:Image\" src=\"https://cdn1.cyclist.co.uk/sites/cyclist/files/styles/gallery_adv/public/2021/02/mj_poc_d2_2021_638.jpg?itok=TaJnWwk8\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<p class=\"gallery-info\"><span>Image 2 of </span>18</p>\n</div> </p>\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-see-related field-type-node-reference field-label-above\">      <div class=\"field-label\">See related&nbsp;</div>\n  \n  <div class=\"field-items\">      <div class=\"field-item even\"><a href=\"/news/9259/van-der-poels-alpecin-fenix-withdraw-from-uae-tour-due-to-covid-positive\">Van der Poel&#039;s Alpecin-Fenix withdraw from UAE Tour due to Covid positive</a></div>      <div class=\"field-item odd\"><a href=\"/news/7774/how-to-watch-the-opening-classics-weekend\">How to watch the opening Classics weekend: Live TV and streaming</a></div>      <div class=\"field-item even\"><a href=\"/news/2252/all-you-need-to-know-about-the-classics-monuments-cobbles\">Cycling Spring Classics 2021: Race dates, Monuments, cobbles and live TV guide</a></div>    </div></div><h3>Weight and price</h3>\n<p>Poc says a size small weighs in at 180g, with a 190g medium and 210g large.</p>\n<p>if you can't wait for the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/tags/ef-education-nippo\">EF Education-Nippo</a> issue bright pink version that's set to debut at the Paris-Nice on March 7th and want to stand out on the road, it's available with bright green straps as well as calmer blue and white, with grey and black options for the shell.</p>\n<p>It's available online and in selected stores for £240.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pocsports.com/collections/cycling-helmets-road/products/ventral-lite\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Buy the Poc Ventral Lite now</strong></em></a> </p>\n  </div>\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-gallery-adv field-type-node-reference field-label-hidden\">  \n  <div class=\"field-items\">      <div class=\"field-item even\">\n<div class=\"node node-gallery-adv gallery-adv-presentation even node-mosaic-large\">\n\n          <><span><a href=\"/news/9264/poc-ventral-lite-photos\">Poc Ventral Lite photos</a></span></>\n      \n  \n  <div class=\"content\">\n\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"field-group-format group_meta group-meta\"><span class=\"field field-name-field-article-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden\">\n      <span class=\"field-item even\"><a href=\"/news\" typeof=\"skos:Concept\" property=\"rdfs:label skos:prefLabel\" datatype=\"\">News</a></span>\n  </span><div class=\"field field-name-field-published-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden\">  \n  <div class=\"field-items\">      <div class=\"field-item even\"><span class=\"date-display-single\" property=\"dc:date\" datatype=\"xsd:dateTime\" content=\"2021-02-23T10:45:00+00:00\">23 Feb 2021</span></div>    </div></div><div  class=\"sharerich-wrapper sharerich-bikesetc-article-default-wrapper sharerich-1\">\n        <div  class=\"item-list\"><ul  class=\"sharerich-buttons rrssb-buttons clearfix\"><li class=\"facebook first\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyclist.co.uk%2Fnews%2F9264%2Fpoc-ventral-lite-photos\" class=\"popup\">\r\n  <span class=\"icon\">\r\n      <svg version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"28px\" height=\"28px\" viewBox=\"0 0 28 28\" enable-background=\"new 0 0 28 28\" xml:space=\"pr